1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:10,000
[English subtitles are available]

2
00:01:36,350 --> 00:01:42,229
[I Don't Want to Be Friends With You]

3
00:01:45,979 --> 00:01:47,210
Have they arrived yet?

4
00:01:48,500 --> 00:01:49,940
-They're coming!
-[This way please.]

5
00:01:51,330 --> 00:01:52,890
Our school usually pays
special attention

6
00:01:52,970 --> 00:01:55,100
to students' all-round development of morality,
intelligence,  physique and aesthetic.

7
00:01:55,539 --> 00:01:57,930
Usually,  there's not much homework left.

8
00:01:58,370 --> 00:01:59,250
Our students...

9
00:02:00,130 --> 00:02:01,210
Hello,  Director!

10
00:02:02,330 --> 00:02:04,490
Let's interview these two students.

11
00:02:06,610 --> 00:02:08,360
The college entrance examination
is around the corner.

12
00:02:08,449 --> 00:02:10,210
Right now,  we are under
intensive schoolwork

13
00:02:10,300 --> 00:02:11,800
and with a large amount of homework.

14
00:02:11,890 --> 00:02:14,080
But to get a good result,

15
00:02:14,170 --> 00:02:15,610
we will all try our best

16
00:02:15,700 --> 00:02:17,290
to honour our school.

17
00:02:19,450 --> 00:02:20,530
It's coming!

18
00:02:21,010 --> 00:02:22,570
-Come on.
-Hurry up.

19
00:02:25,190 --> 00:02:26,510
There it comes.

20
00:02:27,090 --> 00:02:28,840
[The college entrance examination
is around the corner.]

21
00:02:28,930 --> 00:02:30,680
[Right now, we are under
intensive schoolwork]

22
00:02:30,770 --> 00:02:32,370
[and with a large amount of homework.]

23
00:02:32,670 --> 00:02:36,700
[Student Shouts Burden is too Heavy
Graduation Only Leaves a Bitter Memory]

24
00:02:42,100 --> 00:02:43,010
I'm going to cook.

25
00:02:43,810 --> 00:02:44,690
I'll give you a hand.

26
00:02:46,350 --> 00:02:47,490
Write a self-criticism.

27
00:02:49,560 --> 00:02:51,320
[Student Shouts Burden is too Heavy
Graduation Only Leaves a Bitter Memory]

28
00:02:51,320 --> 00:02:57,450
[Episode 14]
[If Graduation Could Carry Sorrows Away]

29
00:03:04,690 --> 00:03:05,650
Not even five minutes have passed.

30
00:03:06,350 --> 00:03:09,210
I'm thinking of one thing
unrelated to study.

31
00:03:12,360 --> 00:03:13,240
And what's that?

32
00:03:14,420 --> 00:03:16,860
How many of you guys
need my tutorship in total?

33
00:03:18,060 --> 00:03:18,940
Stand up!

34
00:03:20,260 --> 00:03:22,650
Hello, Mr Wu.

35
00:03:22,950 --> 00:03:24,250
[Welcome here, Teacher Wu Zhi Xun]

36
00:03:24,930 --> 00:03:25,810
Sit down.

37
00:03:27,300 --> 00:03:28,530
We are a big group of people,

38
00:03:28,620 --> 00:03:30,000
we are afraid to disturb others
in the library,

39
00:03:30,090 --> 00:03:31,650
so I borrowed the Fan family's shop.

40
00:03:32,090 --> 00:03:33,530
It's a bit crowded. I'm sorry.

41
00:03:33,770 --> 00:03:34,650
It's okay.

42
00:03:36,130 --> 00:03:38,250
Each of you reported
their two worst courses,

43
00:03:38,790 --> 00:03:39,770
except you.

44
00:03:39,860 --> 00:03:40,890
Let's start from her.

45
00:03:41,570 --> 00:03:44,050
For me it's Politics and Math.

46
00:03:44,579 --> 00:03:45,780
Math and English.

47
00:03:46,530 --> 00:03:47,930
I'm not good at any course.

48
00:03:48,540 --> 00:03:49,450
Just your worst two.

49
00:03:49,930 --> 00:03:52,060
Math and Geography.

50
00:03:53,450 --> 00:03:54,850
History and Geography.

51
00:03:55,210 --> 00:03:56,200
From now on

52
00:03:56,290 --> 00:03:57,490
until the mock exam,

53
00:03:57,780 --> 00:03:58,850
I'll be tutoring you two courses,

54
00:03:59,100 --> 00:04:00,100
Math and Geography.

55
00:04:00,350 --> 00:04:01,290
Why?

56
00:04:01,370 --> 00:04:02,290
Because for all of you

57
00:04:02,370 --> 00:04:05,050
it's difficult to improve your degree
in a short term,

58
00:04:05,130 --> 00:04:06,610
especially for Duan Xiao and Li Jin Bu.

59
00:04:07,090 --> 00:04:08,610
You two have done a good job,

60
00:04:08,780 --> 00:04:10,290
so there's little room for improvement.

61
00:04:10,780 --> 00:04:11,770
But it is possible.

62
00:04:11,980 --> 00:04:13,620
As long as we focus
on the two worst courses,

63
00:04:13,810 --> 00:04:14,770
we can make it.

64
00:04:15,530 --> 00:04:17,079
It's hard to raise from 70 to 100,

65
00:04:17,170 --> 00:04:19,470
but it's easy to score up from zero to 30.

66
00:04:19,560 --> 00:04:20,440
Right?

67
00:04:24,690 --> 00:04:26,690
Mathematics is the biggest difficulty
for liberal arts students.

68
00:04:26,990 --> 00:04:29,210
And geography is a new-added subject.

69
00:04:29,700 --> 00:04:30,810
It's not that difficult,

70
00:04:30,900 --> 00:04:32,220
but many students are not good at it.

71
00:04:32,730 --> 00:04:34,100
so there is a lot of room for promotion.

72
00:04:34,490 --> 00:04:35,890
Let's start with these two courses.

73
00:04:38,970 --> 00:04:40,050
What do you guys think?

74
00:04:40,900 --> 00:04:43,020
We promise to study hard.

75
00:04:43,130 --> 00:04:44,570
Good. Let's get started then.

76
00:04:56,930 --> 00:04:57,930
What's the matter with your class?

77
00:04:58,300 --> 00:05:00,250
Why don't they make noise
when self-studying?

78
00:05:00,740 --> 00:05:01,620
I told you,

79
00:05:02,080 --> 00:05:03,520
don't look down on their ambitions.

80
00:05:03,810 --> 00:05:04,690
Just wait and see.

81
00:05:22,180 --> 00:05:23,650
Let me treat you when it's over.

82
00:05:24,180 --> 00:05:25,060
Hua.

83
00:05:25,170 --> 00:05:26,050
What would you like to eat?

84
00:05:26,170 --> 00:05:27,490
Don't go out and waste your money.

85
00:05:28,460 --> 00:05:29,660
Let's go home to eat.

86
00:05:30,340 --> 00:05:32,650
Don't mention about spending money
to Li Qing Tong.

87
00:05:32,740 --> 00:05:34,010
She's frugal now.

88
00:05:34,530 --> 00:05:35,409
Look.

89
00:05:36,210 --> 00:05:37,700
This pencil is so short
and she still uses it.

90
00:05:40,850 --> 00:05:42,170
Please be nice to yourself.

91
00:05:42,610 --> 00:05:43,490
It's on me today.

92
00:05:43,930 --> 00:05:44,810
That won't help.

93
00:05:45,250 --> 00:05:46,210
It'll be my treat today.

94
00:05:46,940 --> 00:05:48,770
You have been working hard recently

95
00:05:48,970 --> 00:05:50,090
and this is for encouragement.

96
00:05:51,690 --> 00:05:52,570
Keep doing your homework.

97
00:05:52,690 --> 00:05:53,570
I'll go shopping.

98
00:05:58,890 --> 00:05:59,770
That's weird.

99
00:06:03,660 --> 00:06:05,010
Stop writing guys,

100
00:06:05,100 --> 00:06:07,180
Since the teacher is not here,
let's discuss important matters.

101
00:06:07,940 --> 00:06:08,890
What would that be?

102
00:06:09,620 --> 00:06:11,210
What are we working so hard for?

103
00:06:11,650 --> 00:06:12,970
It's for the School Day performance.

104
00:06:14,690 --> 00:06:16,090
If we're going to perform,

105
00:06:16,170 --> 00:06:17,050
what are we going to show?

106
00:06:18,810 --> 00:06:19,730
We'll show how to finish the test paper?

107
00:06:24,000 --> 00:06:24,880
You are right.

108
00:06:26,340 --> 00:06:27,980
How can we forget this?

109
00:06:29,370 --> 00:06:30,450
I object.

110
00:06:31,450 --> 00:06:32,470
I'm telling you

111
00:06:32,550 --> 00:06:34,760
we should perform
"The Tale of the White Snake".

112
00:06:34,850 --> 00:06:36,250
Meet at the broken bridge.

113
00:06:36,900 --> 00:06:39,130
I will play the role of Bai Su Zhen.

114
00:06:39,980 --> 00:06:41,680
Duan Xiao. You can play Xu Xian's role.

115
00:06:41,770 --> 00:06:42,850
I can do Xiao Qing's part.

116
00:06:44,140 --> 00:06:45,810
Why are you taking Bai Su Zhen's part?

117
00:06:46,260 --> 00:06:47,900
I think Hua can do it better.

118
00:06:48,409 --> 00:06:50,450
How can Bai Su Zhen
have this hairstyle she has?

119
00:06:50,540 --> 00:06:52,060
I'm the only one who can do it.

120
00:06:52,370 --> 00:06:53,690
Then I'd rather to play Fa Hai's role.

121
00:06:54,070 --> 00:06:55,520
Xu Xian's role is fine to me.

122
00:06:55,610 --> 00:06:56,610
I don't mind.

123
00:06:56,860 --> 00:06:58,020
Stop talking.

124
00:06:58,810 --> 00:07:00,220
I'd rather pick "Journey to the West".

125
00:07:00,450 --> 00:07:01,330
"Havoc in Heaven".

126
00:07:02,180 --> 00:07:03,240
I'll play Monkey King

127
00:07:03,330 --> 00:07:04,900
and you guys play the monsters
bullied by me.

128
00:07:04,990 --> 00:07:05,970
Shut up!

129
00:07:06,060 --> 00:07:08,370
Those involved in the fight
are all immortals, no monsters at all.

130
00:07:09,050 --> 00:07:11,450
Can you guys hold the temperament
of the immortals?

131
00:07:11,660 --> 00:07:13,490
Look at you guys,
you have nothing to do with beauty.

132
00:07:14,130 --> 00:07:15,010
I think you can do it.

133
00:07:15,450 --> 00:07:16,570
You'd play Marshal Tian Peng.

134
00:07:16,900 --> 00:07:17,930
Wang Xiao Min!

135
00:07:18,020 --> 00:07:20,080
I'm telling you, I will play Bai Su Zhen.

136
00:07:20,170 --> 00:07:21,350
-"Havoc in Heaven".
-Bai Su Zhen.

137
00:07:21,440 --> 00:07:22,250
"Havoc in Heaven".

138
00:07:22,340 --> 00:07:23,860
I said Bai Su Zhen.
My words don't matter, right?

139
00:07:24,010 --> 00:07:25,330
Bai Su Zhen.

140
00:07:26,180 --> 00:07:27,410
-Am I...
-Don't look at me.

141
00:07:27,940 --> 00:07:29,090
I got it, got it.

142
00:07:29,530 --> 00:07:30,820
-Come on, listen to me you two.
-Stop running, stop.

143
00:07:30,820 --> 00:07:32,970
[Daily Necessity Supermarket
and Restaurant]

144
00:07:32,970 --> 00:07:33,840
So that's the deal.

145
00:07:33,930 --> 00:07:34,810
We'll sing instead.

146
00:07:35,540 --> 00:07:36,570
When was it decided?

147
00:07:37,010 --> 00:07:38,010
Why nobody told me that?

148
00:07:38,210 --> 00:07:39,570
Aren't we deciding this?

149
00:07:40,010 --> 00:07:40,890
Please raise your hand if you agree.

150
00:07:48,409 --> 00:07:49,320
The majority agrees.

151
00:07:49,409 --> 00:07:50,290
Deal.

152
00:07:50,520 --> 00:07:51,400
Wait

153
00:07:51,500 --> 00:07:52,700
Aren't you Bai Su Zhen?

154
00:07:53,490 --> 00:07:55,980
Without Hua cheating everyone,
how can we have this opportunity?

155
00:07:58,210 --> 00:07:59,090
I mean encouragement.

156
00:07:59,300 --> 00:08:02,050
Without Hua encouraging everyone,
how can we get this opportunity?

157
00:08:02,330 --> 00:08:03,840
Hua has definitely the final say.

158
00:08:03,930 --> 00:08:06,340
Since Li Qing Tong said that,
I will definitely support her.

159
00:08:06,900 --> 00:08:07,780
Then let's do it.

160
00:08:08,570 --> 00:08:11,330
I live up to my reputation
as Zhang Xue You in Tieyuan.

161
00:08:12,300 --> 00:08:13,820
But which song do we sing?

162
00:08:14,290 --> 00:08:15,700
I'm thinking about it.

163
00:08:16,650 --> 00:08:18,250
I'll let you know when I get an idea.

164
00:08:27,140 --> 00:08:28,370
What are you doing?

165
00:08:29,220 --> 00:08:30,730
All night in front of a piece
of blank paper.

166
00:08:31,690 --> 00:08:33,090
I'm writing the lyrics.

167
00:08:33,179 --> 00:08:34,450
You know how to write lyrics?

168
00:08:34,850 --> 00:08:36,760
I've been listening to songs
for more than a decade,

169
00:08:36,850 --> 00:08:38,640
and I'd like to write one for us.

170
00:08:38,730 --> 00:08:40,340
You mean creative work?

171
00:08:41,929 --> 00:08:43,419
I wonder if you can do it.

172
00:08:43,770 --> 00:08:45,240
You have to do creative work,

173
00:08:45,330 --> 00:08:47,010
review your lessons,
and rehearse at the same time.

174
00:08:47,700 --> 00:08:49,380
No problem. Don't worry.

175
00:08:52,460 --> 00:08:53,340
Alright,

176
00:08:53,450 --> 00:08:54,330
go for it.

177
00:08:54,540 --> 00:08:56,250
I'll go to sleep. Good night.

178
00:09:01,920 --> 00:09:05,320
[Lyrics]

179
00:09:06,640 --> 00:09:08,050
From now on,
we'll spend 20 minutes rehearsing

180
00:09:08,140 --> 00:09:09,270
and the rest of the time studying.

181
00:09:10,210 --> 00:09:11,410
When shall we have fun then?

182
00:09:12,530 --> 00:09:14,490
All you know is having fun.

183
00:09:14,930 --> 00:09:15,970
Hua said that

184
00:09:16,050 --> 00:09:17,810
one should have ambitions
to prove themselves.

185
00:09:18,400 --> 00:09:19,330
Fine!

186
00:09:19,930 --> 00:09:21,730
This time I'll use my song

187
00:09:22,020 --> 00:09:22,970
to prove myself.

188
00:10:27,250 --> 00:10:28,130
What happened to you?

189
00:10:29,050 --> 00:10:31,160
I was thinking
it would be nice to have a guitar.

190
00:10:31,460 --> 00:10:32,690
What do you want a guitar for?

191
00:10:33,340 --> 00:10:35,050
I want to play it on the School Day.

192
00:10:35,330 --> 00:10:36,570
You can play the guitar?

193
00:10:37,430 --> 00:10:38,360
A little bit.

194
00:10:38,450 --> 00:10:39,850
I've learnt online by myself.

195
00:10:43,180 --> 00:10:45,730
[Tieyuan No. 3 Middle School]

196
00:10:48,060 --> 00:10:49,060
Do you have a guitar?

197
00:10:49,290 --> 00:10:50,260
Nope.

198
00:10:50,330 --> 00:10:52,560
What about your friends?

199
00:10:52,650 --> 00:10:54,080
Neither do they.

200
00:10:54,170 --> 00:10:56,410
Why don't you ask Li Qiang?

201
00:10:59,980 --> 00:11:01,440
Li Qiang. Do you have a guitar?

202
00:11:01,530 --> 00:11:02,410
No.

203
00:11:08,730 --> 00:11:09,860
What do you want a guitar for?

204
00:11:18,020 --> 00:11:18,900
Here it is.

205
00:11:19,890 --> 00:11:20,970
How come you have this?

206
00:11:21,050 --> 00:11:21,970
Can you play the guitar?

207
00:11:22,570 --> 00:11:23,450
No, I can't.

208
00:11:24,380 --> 00:11:26,130
Niu Xiao Huo gave it to me
when he was leaving.

209
00:11:26,210 --> 00:11:27,490
Who knows what he was thinking about.

210
00:11:27,970 --> 00:11:30,540
I guess he wanted me to use it
when dealing with girls.

211
00:11:30,900 --> 00:11:32,620
Fine.
Thank you.

212
00:11:33,370 --> 00:11:34,250
Is anybody here?

213
00:11:34,940 --> 00:11:35,820
Coming.

214
00:11:36,500 --> 00:11:40,130
♫ The red fence reflects the setting sun ♫

215
00:11:40,270 --> 00:11:44,120
♫ A piece of note makes my mind go ♫

216
00:11:44,210 --> 00:11:48,290
♫ Autumn wind sweeps fallen leaves
across the playground ♫

217
00:11:48,390 --> 00:11:52,220
♫ The schoolbag is left on ♫

218
00:11:55,860 --> 00:11:56,740
Such a lovely song.

219
00:11:57,770 --> 00:11:59,170
Hua, you're a genius.

220
00:11:59,260 --> 00:12:00,810
How can you do everything?

221
00:12:01,400 --> 00:12:02,280
Hua.

222
00:12:02,390 --> 00:12:03,720
Your song sounds good,

223
00:12:03,810 --> 00:12:05,300
but not exciting enough.

224
00:12:05,610 --> 00:12:07,060
Can you sing Zhang Xue You's song?

225
00:12:07,620 --> 00:12:08,530
Zhang Xin Zhe's song, please.

226
00:12:09,280 --> 00:12:11,730
I'm not familiar with these two singers.

227
00:12:13,340 --> 00:12:14,730
You're too old-fashioned.

228
00:12:15,740 --> 00:12:19,780
[Tieyuan No. 3 Middle School]

229
00:12:20,180 --> 00:12:22,050
Why did you take me here
instead of going home after school?

230
00:12:22,140 --> 00:12:23,020
Please wait a moment.

231
00:12:24,460 --> 00:12:25,340
Uncle Chang Sheng

232
00:12:26,540 --> 00:12:27,420
Xiao.

233
00:12:31,450 --> 00:12:32,810
This is my schoolmate Chen Jun He.

234
00:12:32,890 --> 00:12:34,410
This my father's comrades in arms,
uncle Chang Sheng.

235
00:12:34,600 --> 00:12:35,480
Nice to meet you.

236
00:12:35,810 --> 00:12:37,600
Uncle Chang Sheng has been repairing
watches for generations.

237
00:12:37,690 --> 00:12:39,190
He can repair all kinds of watches.
He's a pro.

238
00:12:39,270 --> 00:12:40,890
Where is the watch? Show it.

239
00:12:45,460 --> 00:12:46,810
This watch has a certain age,

240
00:12:47,270 --> 00:12:48,170
and it's rare.

241
00:12:48,460 --> 00:12:50,170
Uncle, can it be fixed?

242
00:12:57,260 --> 00:12:58,140
It's not a big deal.

243
00:12:58,250 --> 00:12:59,170
Leave it to me.

244
00:12:59,270 --> 00:13:00,980
When it's fixed,
I'll let Xiao come to pick it.

245
00:13:01,780 --> 00:13:02,660
Thank you.

246
00:13:03,100 --> 00:13:04,040
You're welcome.

247
00:13:04,130 --> 00:13:05,180
Since you two are friends,

248
00:13:05,400 --> 00:13:06,970
I regard you as my own child.

249
00:13:07,560 --> 00:13:08,800
-I'm leaving now.
-Okay.

250
00:13:08,900 --> 00:13:09,730
See you, Uncle.

251
00:13:09,810 --> 00:13:11,020
-Goodbye, Uncle.
-Take care.

252
00:13:14,450 --> 00:13:15,330
Thanks.

253
00:13:15,890 --> 00:13:16,820
No worries.

254
00:13:16,890 --> 00:13:17,770
You lent me your guitar.

255
00:13:17,890 --> 00:13:18,770
I'm paying you back.

256
00:13:21,170 --> 00:13:22,050
Okay.

257
00:13:22,460 --> 00:13:24,690
Let's play basketball together
when you're free.

258
00:13:25,570 --> 00:13:26,450
No problem.

259
00:13:27,650 --> 00:13:28,530
I'm leaving.

260
00:13:32,020 --> 00:13:35,620
[Good luck]

261
00:13:37,270 --> 00:13:38,530
Mum, I'm going out.

262
00:13:39,450 --> 00:13:40,330
Where are you going?

263
00:13:41,090 --> 00:13:41,970
To the library.

264
00:13:42,380 --> 00:13:44,050
Don't lie to me like before.

265
00:13:59,180 --> 00:14:00,060
There you are.

266
00:14:01,010 --> 00:14:02,730
Sorry, I'm late.

267
00:14:13,700 --> 00:14:15,650
Let's have something to eat
when it's over.

268
00:14:16,330 --> 00:14:17,610
Last time it was your treat.

269
00:14:17,700 --> 00:14:19,370
This time it's ours.

270
00:14:19,660 --> 00:14:20,570
Okay.

271
00:14:21,450 --> 00:14:22,330
What do you want to eat?

272
00:14:22,900 --> 00:14:23,870
Everything is fine for me.

273
00:14:23,970 --> 00:14:24,970
Whatever.

274
00:14:25,130 --> 00:14:26,050
I want to eat hot pot.

275
00:14:26,730 --> 00:14:28,090
No way. I want to have barbecue.

276
00:14:29,660 --> 00:14:31,330
Only buffet is right for you two.

277
00:14:31,610 --> 00:14:34,120
As for all the buffets in Tieyuan,
with no exception,

278
00:14:34,210 --> 00:14:35,690
only you two can eat them.

279
00:14:40,340 --> 00:14:41,210
Wu Zhi Xun.

280
00:14:41,290 --> 00:14:42,730
This is the first time
I see you laugh like this.

281
00:14:43,690 --> 00:14:44,570
Really?

282
00:14:47,290 --> 00:14:48,170
To be honest,

283
00:14:48,580 --> 00:14:49,730
I envy you guys.

284
00:14:50,900 --> 00:14:52,410
I've never had so many friends.

285
00:14:53,490 --> 00:14:54,770
Since junior high school,

286
00:14:55,010 --> 00:14:56,420
I haven't had any friend.

287
00:14:56,740 --> 00:14:58,290
Such a pity.

288
00:15:00,260 --> 00:15:01,640
You can hang out with us later,

289
00:15:01,730 --> 00:15:02,790
we're all your friends.

290
00:15:02,870 --> 00:15:03,750
Yeah.

291
00:15:04,020 --> 00:15:06,170
Well... I accept you, too.

292
00:15:07,300 --> 00:15:08,690
Can you be nice?

293
00:15:09,250 --> 00:15:10,380
Just kidding.

294
00:15:19,210 --> 00:15:20,090
Dad.

295
00:15:20,740 --> 00:15:21,940
Who's Li Qing Tong?

296
00:15:27,810 --> 00:15:28,690
That's me.

297
00:15:30,330 --> 00:15:31,690
You look very honest,

298
00:15:32,410 --> 00:15:34,330
but why do you keep bothering him?

299
00:15:34,770 --> 00:15:36,570
Dad. What are you talking about?

300
00:15:36,660 --> 00:15:37,570
None of your business!

301
00:15:39,100 --> 00:15:39,980
Miss Li.

302
00:15:40,660 --> 00:15:43,330
I know Wu Zhi Xun is helping you
with your homework.

303
00:15:43,650 --> 00:15:44,530
I also believed

304
00:15:45,090 --> 00:15:47,020
you knew the importance of studying,
at least.

305
00:15:47,780 --> 00:15:49,610
But when I asked about your performance
at school,

306
00:15:50,170 --> 00:15:51,690
it really surprised me.

307
00:15:52,100 --> 00:15:52,980
Dad.

308
00:15:54,130 --> 00:15:55,010
Wu Zhi Xun

309
00:15:55,130 --> 00:15:56,580
plans to enter a top-ranked school.

310
00:15:56,850 --> 00:15:58,850
He has no time to have fun with you.

311
00:15:59,340 --> 00:16:00,450
Especially with you.

312
00:16:00,540 --> 00:16:01,660
A child who is unruly

313
00:16:02,130 --> 00:16:03,250
and without sense of decency.

314
00:16:03,980 --> 00:16:04,890
You'd better stay away from him.

315
00:16:05,010 --> 00:16:05,890
Wu Yi Jin!

316
00:16:07,170 --> 00:16:08,140
What did you call me?

317
00:16:12,050 --> 00:16:12,930
Come back!

318
00:16:24,170 --> 00:16:25,690
That is unpleasant to hear.

319
00:16:26,100 --> 00:16:27,330
If he hadn't been Wu Zhi Xun's father,

320
00:16:27,690 --> 00:16:28,970
I would have beaten him.

321
00:16:29,380 --> 00:16:30,820
Why weren't you so fierce just now?

322
00:16:32,290 --> 00:16:33,730
I'm protecting Li Qing Tong's face.

323
00:16:36,170 --> 00:16:37,490
Are you okay?

324
00:16:38,770 --> 00:16:39,730
Don't think about it.

325
00:16:40,260 --> 00:16:41,730
His dad doesn't look good at all.

326
00:16:41,820 --> 00:16:42,700
Who cares what he says.

327
00:16:45,610 --> 00:16:46,730
Never mind.

328
00:16:48,740 --> 00:16:49,810
But I just worry that...

329
00:16:50,940 --> 00:16:53,610
Is Wu Zhi Xun going to fight with his dad
again as he went back like this?

330
00:16:54,530 --> 00:16:55,410
With such a dad,

331
00:16:55,690 --> 00:16:57,010
it's hard not to quarrel.

332
00:16:57,160 --> 00:16:58,130
I agree.

333
00:16:58,220 --> 00:17:00,570
Scolding his son's classmate
without making it clear.

334
00:17:01,060 --> 00:17:02,820
I would rather not have a dad
than one like him.

335
00:17:05,170 --> 00:17:06,050
It's okay.

336
00:17:27,260 --> 00:17:28,140
Pick your bag up!

337
00:17:28,410 --> 00:17:29,290
Pick it up!

338
00:17:30,690 --> 00:17:31,660
What happened to you?

339
00:17:32,250 --> 00:17:33,420
Ask your son.

340
00:17:33,690 --> 00:17:35,250
He called me by my full name outside.

341
00:17:35,450 --> 00:17:37,060
Come on! Try saying it again!

342
00:17:37,650 --> 00:17:38,570
Calm down.

343
00:17:38,650 --> 00:17:40,460
Aren't you afraid that our neighbours
will laugh at us?

344
00:17:40,730 --> 00:17:41,810
Please leave.

345
00:17:42,050 --> 00:17:43,170
I'm going to study.

346
00:17:43,660 --> 00:17:45,370
I can discipline you, can't I?

347
00:17:45,980 --> 00:17:46,890
Please stop.

348
00:17:47,970 --> 00:17:50,020
I don't think
you need to go to school anymore.

349
00:17:50,730 --> 00:17:51,610
Stop being angry.

350
00:17:56,650 --> 00:17:59,890
[Tieyuan No. 3 Middle School]

351
00:18:04,410 --> 00:18:05,610
Attention please.

352
00:18:06,010 --> 00:18:07,450
Because of some special situation

353
00:18:07,740 --> 00:18:09,250
in the family,

354
00:18:09,450 --> 00:18:11,260
Wu Zhi Xun won't attend class
starting from today.

355
00:18:11,530 --> 00:18:12,530
You don't need to worry.

356
00:18:12,830 --> 00:18:13,900
There are only 60 days left.

357
00:18:14,250 --> 00:18:15,370
We can't afford to relax.

358
00:18:15,690 --> 00:18:16,570
We still have to work hard.

359
00:18:17,050 --> 00:18:19,180
Take out the examination paper.
Let's explain it.

360
00:18:22,820 --> 00:18:23,700
Mr Wu.

361
00:18:24,610 --> 00:18:26,340
What happened to Wu Zhi Xun?

362
00:18:26,930 --> 00:18:28,370
His parents came to school a few days ago

363
00:18:28,610 --> 00:18:30,090
and said they had a tutor for him.

364
00:18:30,300 --> 00:18:31,510
Since there are no lessons now,

365
00:18:31,620 --> 00:18:32,500
only the review,

366
00:18:32,770 --> 00:18:34,330
I have no reason to say no to his parents.

367
00:18:34,970 --> 00:18:36,810
But this is quite sudden.

368
00:18:37,690 --> 00:18:39,450
If you're worried, you can go to visit him.

369
00:18:39,540 --> 00:18:40,570
As for other things,

370
00:18:40,930 --> 00:18:41,930
there's no need to worry.

371
00:18:42,060 --> 00:18:42,940
Go ahead.

372
00:18:49,490 --> 00:18:50,810
Don't go look for him.

373
00:18:51,540 --> 00:18:53,690
His dad won't let him see you.

374
00:19:08,090 --> 00:19:09,730
[So Wu Zhi Xun never came to class.]

375
00:19:10,050 --> 00:19:11,570
[He never came to school after that.]

376
00:19:12,020 --> 00:19:14,360
[For most classmates in our class,]

377
00:19:14,450 --> 00:19:16,500
[there is no difference
whether he's here or not.]

378
00:19:16,640 --> 00:19:18,540
[Except for being the top student,]

379
00:19:18,730 --> 00:19:20,810
[he has no sense of existence
and he's not popular.]

380
00:19:20,900 --> 00:19:22,020
[No one misses him.]

381
00:19:29,290 --> 00:19:30,850
What does this word mean?

382
00:19:36,540 --> 00:19:37,410
[Except...]

383
00:19:37,490 --> 00:19:38,620
[Except Li Qing Tong.]

384
00:19:39,180 --> 00:19:41,120
[After Wu Zhi Xun's disappearance,]

385
00:19:41,210 --> 00:19:43,020
[she seems like she has lost her soul.]

386
00:19:43,460 --> 00:19:44,340
[Perhaps,]

387
00:19:44,580 --> 00:19:47,130
[she put most of the blame on herself.]

388
00:19:50,080 --> 00:19:53,510
♫ She always leaves
only the phone number ♫

389
00:19:53,610 --> 00:19:57,100
♫ She never let me take her home ♫

390
00:20:13,970 --> 00:20:14,940
That answer must be D.

391
00:20:15,210 --> 00:20:16,840
I think is B.
The answer of the fourth question is D.

392
00:20:16,930 --> 00:20:17,810
You can ask them.

393
00:20:18,140 --> 00:20:19,020
I think is B.

394
00:20:19,290 --> 00:20:20,160
Are you sure?

395
00:20:20,250 --> 00:20:21,130
Why are you so slow?

396
00:20:21,740 --> 00:20:23,180
I checked many times.

397
00:20:23,540 --> 00:20:24,750
This is the decisive battle.

398
00:20:24,840 --> 00:20:25,800
How did you do in the exam?

399
00:20:25,890 --> 00:20:26,880
I think I did okay.

400
00:20:26,970 --> 00:20:28,080
I think I did quite well.

401
00:20:28,170 --> 00:20:29,570
All the questions were those
Wu Zhi Xun had explained.

402
00:20:29,650 --> 00:20:30,530
Don't worry.

403
00:20:36,650 --> 00:20:38,080
How about you? You did okay?

404
00:20:38,170 --> 00:20:39,170
What do you think?

405
00:20:43,830 --> 00:20:45,690
Just take care of yourself.

406
00:20:59,730 --> 00:21:00,610
Who's there?

407
00:21:01,210 --> 00:21:02,930
Is Wu Zhi Xun home?

408
00:21:03,410 --> 00:21:04,290
Who are you?

409
00:21:04,900 --> 00:21:06,570
I'm his classmate.

410
00:21:06,830 --> 00:21:08,180
My name is Li Qing Tong.

411
00:21:09,210 --> 00:21:10,090
He's not home.

412
00:21:10,680 --> 00:21:11,740
Then...

413
00:21:11,820 --> 00:21:13,930
When will he come back to class?

414
00:21:29,450 --> 00:21:30,530
The result of the third mock exam
came out.

415
00:21:31,420 --> 00:21:34,010
First, let's announce the answer
you care the most about.

416
00:21:35,290 --> 00:21:36,170
Lin Xue Wei.

417
00:21:37,290 --> 00:21:38,410
514 points.

418
00:21:39,490 --> 00:21:41,540
31 points higher
than the second mock exam.

419
00:21:43,010 --> 00:21:43,890
Zhao Xiao Na.

420
00:21:44,300 --> 00:21:45,380
462 points.

421
00:21:45,840 --> 00:21:48,020
33 points higher
than the second mock exam.

422
00:21:48,900 --> 00:21:49,850
Wang Xiao Min.

423
00:21:50,660 --> 00:21:51,930
398 points.

424
00:21:52,250 --> 00:21:53,990
You've improved by

425
00:21:54,080 --> 00:21:55,250
45 points.

426
00:22:00,810 --> 00:22:02,420
The starting point is not high.

427
00:22:04,420 --> 00:22:05,410
Li Qing Tong.

428
00:22:07,620 --> 00:22:09,580
You are always at the bottom of our class.

429
00:22:10,140 --> 00:22:11,490
What do you think about this time?

430
00:22:12,570 --> 00:22:13,450
Li Qing Tong.

431
00:22:13,780 --> 00:22:14,890
412 points.

432
00:22:15,180 --> 00:22:16,890
You've improved by

433
00:22:17,500 --> 00:22:18,380
61 points.

434
00:22:22,580 --> 00:22:23,590
Congratulations!

435
00:22:23,690 --> 00:22:26,490
You've advanced the most
in our class this time.

436
00:22:28,500 --> 00:22:29,380
Chen Jun He.

437
00:22:30,730 --> 00:22:31,610
402 points.

438
00:22:32,580 --> 00:22:34,250
30 points higher
than the second mock exam.

439
00:22:35,900 --> 00:22:37,750
So far, all of you
have reached the standard.

440
00:22:37,830 --> 00:22:38,770
The last one.

441
00:22:39,840 --> 00:22:41,130
Li Jin Bu.

442
00:22:42,140 --> 00:22:43,330
511 points.

443
00:22:44,260 --> 00:22:46,010
You've improved by

444
00:22:48,660 --> 00:22:49,540
27 points.

445
00:22:52,450 --> 00:22:53,330
Three points less.

446
00:22:54,380 --> 00:22:55,290
Class begins.

447
00:23:20,460 --> 00:23:22,160
It's okay, Hua.

448
00:23:22,250 --> 00:23:24,010
It's not a big deal.

449
00:23:27,330 --> 00:23:28,260
It's all my fault.

450
00:23:28,970 --> 00:23:30,460
I've held everyone back.

451
00:23:30,690 --> 00:23:31,930
It's just 3 points.

452
00:23:32,370 --> 00:23:34,160
Everyone knows you've tried your best.

453
00:23:34,250 --> 00:23:35,240
That's right, Hua.

454
00:23:35,330 --> 00:23:36,290
No one blames you.

455
00:23:36,970 --> 00:23:38,580
I used to laugh at you every day.

456
00:23:39,020 --> 00:23:41,050
It turns out I've dropped away
at the critical moment.

457
00:23:41,460 --> 00:23:42,400
I'm a loser.

458
00:23:42,490 --> 00:23:43,400
Don't say nonsense.

459
00:23:43,490 --> 00:23:45,530
I'll beat those who dare say you're loser.

460
00:23:45,620 --> 00:23:47,180
Don't add fuel to the fire.

461
00:23:50,770 --> 00:23:51,650
Hua.

462
00:23:52,050 --> 00:23:53,130
Forget it.

463
00:24:01,730 --> 00:24:03,490
How about this? I'll beg Mr Wu.

464
00:24:15,410 --> 00:24:16,290
Monitor,

465
00:24:16,540 --> 00:24:17,930
everyone has done their best.

466
00:24:18,690 --> 00:24:19,570
That's right.

467
00:24:19,980 --> 00:24:22,130
So there is nothing to regret.

468
00:24:22,380 --> 00:24:24,090
It's just a literary performance.

469
00:24:24,330 --> 00:24:25,580
Yet, we don't cherish it.

470
00:24:28,170 --> 00:24:29,050
Li Jin Bu,

471
00:24:29,220 --> 00:24:30,650
you really don't have to be sad anymore.

472
00:24:30,890 --> 00:24:33,060
We've done a great job.

473
00:24:33,380 --> 00:24:35,580
There is no class that can be like ours.

474
00:24:35,970 --> 00:24:38,720
Now the whole school
has been impressed by us.

475
00:24:38,810 --> 00:24:40,250
This is all because of you.

476
00:24:41,010 --> 00:24:41,890
What's more,

477
00:24:41,980 --> 00:24:43,480
it's just a literary performance.

478
00:24:43,570 --> 00:24:45,330
It doesn't matter
if we participate or not.

479
00:24:45,700 --> 00:24:47,760
It's not a big deal.

480
00:24:47,850 --> 00:24:49,250
Let's perform in our class on School Day.

481
00:24:49,660 --> 00:24:50,540
Yeah.

482
00:24:52,220 --> 00:24:53,100
Don't be sad.

483
00:24:56,060 --> 00:24:56,940
That's right.

484
00:24:57,650 --> 00:24:58,810
Let's perform in our class.

485
00:25:00,720 --> 00:25:06,850
[Tieyuan No. 3 Middle School]
[20th Anniversary]

486
00:25:09,770 --> 00:25:11,210
Mr Wu is too cruel.

487
00:25:11,370 --> 00:25:12,490
He's one point short

488
00:25:12,580 --> 00:25:14,330
and he takes it so seriously.

489
00:25:15,300 --> 00:25:17,210
I take back all the praise I gave him.

490
00:25:17,530 --> 00:25:18,940
Please shut up.

491
00:25:20,110 --> 00:25:21,130
Exactly.

492
00:25:21,210 --> 00:25:22,080
Don't be sad.

493
00:25:22,170 --> 00:25:23,570
Haven't we're all agreed on that?

494
00:25:23,780 --> 00:25:25,040
We'll perform in our class tomorrow.

495
00:25:25,130 --> 00:25:26,300
Who cares about them?

496
00:25:28,180 --> 00:25:29,570
Look at you.

497
00:25:30,620 --> 00:25:31,580
Come back to the classroom.

498
00:25:43,700 --> 00:25:45,410
Who's ready for the show?
Raise your hand, please.

499
00:25:47,100 --> 00:25:47,980
I'm asking you.

500
00:25:55,290 --> 00:25:56,210
Can you make it tomorrow?

501
00:25:59,420 --> 00:26:00,630
I'm asking you.

502
00:26:00,720 --> 00:26:02,310
I'll say no to the headmaster
if you can't.

503
00:26:02,740 --> 00:26:04,530
-We can do it!
-We can.

504
00:26:06,930 --> 00:26:07,810
Get ready.

505
00:26:09,050 --> 00:26:10,050
Don't put disgrace on our class.

506
00:26:34,370 --> 00:26:35,250
Come on.

