549
00:29:41,650 --> 00:29:44,010
♫ That is the haven ♫

550
00:29:44,100 --> 00:29:46,680
♫ As for my haven ♫

551
00:29:46,770 --> 00:29:49,000
♫ It's where my friends are ♫

552
00:29:49,090 --> 00:29:51,640
♫ Finally I've found a safe haven ♫

553
00:29:51,730 --> 00:29:54,020
♫ Innocent and happy ♫

554
00:29:54,140 --> 00:29:56,720
♫ Take advantage of youth
to move forward ♫

555
00:29:56,810 --> 00:29:59,770
♫ No matter how crazy we are ♫

556
00:30:01,180 --> 00:30:04,810
♫ That's the best time in our life ♫

557
00:30:32,420 --> 00:30:41,660
[Honour]

558
00:30:41,660 --> 00:30:43,810
Dear students, tomorrow
is the college entrance examination.

559
00:30:44,770 --> 00:30:45,650
In fact,

560
00:30:46,060 --> 00:30:46,940
it's your battle.

561
00:30:47,330 --> 00:30:49,140
We've spent days and nights
together for three years

562
00:30:49,730 --> 00:30:51,410
and prepared for more than 1000 days.

563
00:30:52,420 --> 00:30:53,300
For tomorrow,

564
00:30:53,570 --> 00:30:54,740
you've tried your best.

565
00:30:55,210 --> 00:30:56,680
Whether you do well

566
00:30:56,770 --> 00:30:57,650
or not,

567
00:30:59,650 --> 00:31:00,900
you should be proud.

568
00:31:01,530 --> 00:31:03,660
Not only you should be proud.
I should be too.

569
00:31:04,010 --> 00:31:05,620
It's been my pleasure

570
00:31:06,450 --> 00:31:08,260
to fight with you.

571
00:31:08,630 --> 00:31:09,730
You are soldiers.

572
00:31:10,290 --> 00:31:11,170
As a soldier,

573
00:31:11,610 --> 00:31:13,290
for the ideal
that I hold dear to my heart,

574
00:31:13,900 --> 00:31:15,300
I will not regret a thousand times to die.

575
00:31:15,590 --> 00:31:16,480
Soldiers.

576
00:31:16,570 --> 00:31:17,450
Tomorrow,

577
00:31:17,860 --> 00:31:20,730
give satisfactory answers
for your hard work.

578
00:31:20,820 --> 00:31:21,920
Are you confident?

579
00:31:22,210 --> 00:31:23,530
Yes!

580
00:31:23,780 --> 00:31:25,340
Please give satisfactory answers

581
00:31:25,730 --> 00:31:26,690
for your parents.

582
00:31:26,980 --> 00:31:27,940
Are you confident?

583
00:31:28,020 --> 00:31:28,890
Yes!

584
00:31:28,980 --> 00:31:30,090
Face the college entrance examination

585
00:31:30,430 --> 00:31:31,310
and come back with glory.

586
00:31:31,400 --> 00:31:32,410
Are you confident?

587
00:31:32,500 --> 00:31:33,420
Yes!

588
00:31:33,510 --> 00:31:34,390
Good.

589
00:31:35,250 --> 00:31:36,130
As for me,

590
00:31:36,340 --> 00:31:37,220
I'll be here

591
00:31:37,730 --> 00:31:39,300
waiting for your success.

592
00:31:41,740 --> 00:31:42,620
Class is over.

593
00:31:43,740 --> 00:31:47,770
[Honour]

594
00:31:57,290 --> 00:31:58,170
What are you doing?

595
00:31:59,610 --> 00:32:00,490
Why are you here?

596
00:32:01,330 --> 00:32:02,210
I've come to see you.

597
00:32:02,690 --> 00:32:03,730
Go back.

598
00:32:03,810 --> 00:32:04,820
Tomorrow's
the college entrance examination.

599
00:32:05,290 --> 00:32:06,330
Go back and have an early rest.

600
00:32:06,530 --> 00:32:07,960
That's why I've come here.

601
00:32:08,050 --> 00:32:08,930
I'm afraid you're nervous.

602
00:32:09,020 --> 00:32:09,900
I've come to cheer you up.

603
00:32:10,250 --> 00:32:11,360
I'm okay.

604
00:32:11,450 --> 00:32:13,010
I'm in a good mood.

605
00:32:14,370 --> 00:32:15,240
I'm leaving then.

606
00:32:15,330 --> 00:32:16,210
Wait a minute.

607
00:32:20,250 --> 00:32:21,280
I'm feeling

608
00:32:21,370 --> 00:32:22,860
a little bit nervous now.

609
00:32:23,300 --> 00:32:24,690
I need you to comfort me.

610
00:32:25,070 --> 00:32:25,530
[Victory]

611
00:32:25,530 --> 00:32:26,410
I wish you good luck in the exam.

612
00:32:31,850 --> 00:32:33,330
Don't let your mum down.

613
00:32:35,010 --> 00:32:36,180
Good luck to you too.

614
00:32:36,810 --> 00:32:38,330
Alright, I'm leaving.

615
00:32:47,530 --> 00:32:50,520
[Attention: Relevant Staff for the Examination
Enter with Credentials. No Parents.]

616
00:33:02,010 --> 00:33:03,130
Cheer up.

617
00:33:03,210 --> 00:33:04,140
Stop always eating snacks.

618
00:33:04,300 --> 00:33:05,400
Mind your own business.

619
00:33:05,690 --> 00:33:06,570
Don't fail in the examination.

620
00:33:06,900 --> 00:33:07,780
Impossible.

621
00:33:08,770 --> 00:33:10,300
It's almost time, are you still reciting?

622
00:33:14,940 --> 00:33:18,250
[So, the day of the final judgment
has come.]

623
00:33:18,660 --> 00:33:20,050
[Just like Mr Wu said,]

624
00:33:20,190 --> 00:33:21,730
[the college entrance examination
is a battle.]

625
00:33:21,980 --> 00:33:23,120
Only the hard work

626
00:33:23,250 --> 00:33:24,290
can make you successful.

627
00:33:25,530 --> 00:33:26,410
But who can ignore

628
00:33:27,170 --> 00:33:28,810
the result?

629
00:33:35,330 --> 00:33:39,150
[Tieyuan No. 8 Middle School]

630
00:33:48,490 --> 00:33:50,050
Look at you, did you do well in the exam?

631
00:33:52,040 --> 00:33:53,160
What do you want to hear from me?

632
00:33:53,300 --> 00:33:55,130
Nothing.

633
00:33:55,860 --> 00:33:56,740
Fine, I'll shut up.

634
00:33:57,060 --> 00:33:59,170
I wrote a letter for you all.

635
00:33:59,850 --> 00:34:01,020
Have a look at it.

636
00:34:01,100 --> 00:34:01,280
hang it on the wall and frame it.

637
00:34:01,280 --> 00:34:02,040
[Li Qing Tong]

638
00:34:02,900 --> 00:34:03,780
If you don't,

639
00:34:04,010 --> 00:34:06,180
I'll be angry when I visit your house.

640
00:34:09,530 --> 00:34:10,409
I declare that

641
00:34:11,730 --> 00:34:14,409
all the students in Class three, Grade
three of No.3 Middle School of Tieyuan

642
00:34:15,010 --> 00:34:16,739
have completed their high school studies.

643
00:34:17,330 --> 00:34:18,210
Congratulations!

644
00:34:18,650 --> 00:34:19,530
You've graduated from high school.

645
00:34:26,810 --> 00:34:27,929
"Dear Mr Wu,

646
00:34:28,330 --> 00:34:33,170
after three years of observation and
assessment from all students in Class three,

647
00:34:33,290 --> 00:34:34,280
we unanimously consider you,

648
00:34:34,370 --> 00:34:35,770
Wu Di Bao,

649
00:34:35,850 --> 00:34:37,449
the best, funniest

650
00:34:37,540 --> 00:34:39,489
and most impressive teacher in the world.

651
00:34:40,090 --> 00:34:42,500
We hereby issue you with a medal,

652
00:34:44,010 --> 00:34:45,290
a certificate of award,

653
00:34:46,139 --> 00:34:47,929
a high-quality fountain pen,

654
00:34:48,850 --> 00:34:51,530
and a T-shirt signed
by all students in the class.

655
00:34:53,409 --> 00:34:56,320
We hope Wu Di Bao
will make persistent efforts

656
00:34:56,409 --> 00:34:58,720
to get the title of Excellent Teacher
as soon as possible

657
00:34:58,810 --> 00:35:00,220
and find a girlfriend."

658
00:35:06,310 --> 00:35:07,980
Thank you. Thank you very much.

659
00:35:08,050 --> 00:35:08,930
Stand up.

660
00:35:10,810 --> 00:35:11,690
Mr Wu.

661
00:35:11,890 --> 00:35:13,650
We have something to say.

662
00:35:13,740 --> 00:35:14,620
Mr Wu.

663
00:35:15,130 --> 00:35:18,210
Thank you for bearing with us
when we make mistakes.

664
00:35:18,530 --> 00:35:19,410
Mr Wu.

665
00:35:19,900 --> 00:35:22,480
Thank you for pleading with the headmaster

666
00:35:22,570 --> 00:35:24,300
in order to let us take part
in the performance.

667
00:35:24,660 --> 00:35:25,540
Mr Wu.

668
00:35:26,090 --> 00:35:26,970
Thank you

669
00:35:27,210 --> 00:35:29,210
for not giving up on us
when we made mistakes.

670
00:35:29,820 --> 00:35:30,900
Mr Wu.

671
00:35:31,050 --> 00:35:31,930
Thank you

672
00:35:32,090 --> 00:35:35,300
for not telling our parents
about our poor performance at school.

673
00:35:36,100 --> 00:35:36,980
Mr Wu.

674
00:35:37,450 --> 00:35:38,890
It was a pleasure meeting you.

675
00:35:39,260 --> 00:35:40,820
I hope you won't forget us.

676
00:35:41,140 --> 00:35:42,460
We won't forget you either.

677
00:35:43,140 --> 00:35:44,330
Three, two,

678
00:35:44,410 --> 00:35:45,280
one.

679
00:35:45,370 --> 00:35:47,450
Dear Mr Wu,

680
00:35:47,540 --> 00:35:49,210
thank you.

681
00:35:49,410 --> 00:35:52,020
We'll love you forever.

682
00:35:52,330 --> 00:35:53,250
Thank you very much.

683
00:35:54,770 --> 00:35:57,580
[Dear Mr Wu, thank you]

684
00:36:07,160 --> 00:36:10,010
[Wu Di Bao]

685
00:36:10,010 --> 00:36:19,920
[Signatures of the whole class]

686
00:36:19,920 --> 00:36:20,250
[Aim Higher, Youth Dream Deserved]

687
00:36:20,250 --> 00:36:21,490
[Every year on this stage]

688
00:36:22,740 --> 00:36:24,650
[I send off a group of graduates.]

689
00:36:26,020 --> 00:36:27,130
[Two months later]

690
00:36:27,210 --> 00:36:29,010
[I'd welcome another group
of new students.]

691
00:36:29,540 --> 00:36:30,690
That's my job.

692
00:36:31,050 --> 00:36:32,300
And also my life.

693
00:36:34,250 --> 00:36:37,410
Every adult plays a different role.

694
00:36:38,290 --> 00:36:39,690
Someone is as kind and nice

695
00:36:39,780 --> 00:36:40,980
as a brother next door.

696
00:36:41,780 --> 00:36:42,970
Someone takes care of you

697
00:36:43,050 --> 00:36:44,130
like your parents would.

698
00:36:44,980 --> 00:36:46,410
Someone is naughty

699
00:36:46,770 --> 00:36:47,970
as your childhood playmate.

700
00:36:49,210 --> 00:36:50,090
In addition,

701
00:36:50,930 --> 00:36:51,960
someone is strict,

702
00:36:52,050 --> 00:36:53,050
rational,

703
00:36:53,420 --> 00:36:54,490
and disturbing.

704
00:36:55,420 --> 00:36:58,770
They'd remind you all the time
that the road of life is not smooth.

705
00:36:59,140 --> 00:37:00,330
Don't resist growth.

706
00:37:01,260 --> 00:37:02,140
If you want to grow,

707
00:37:02,690 --> 00:37:03,980
you have to go through the storm.

708
00:37:05,050 --> 00:37:06,300
There must be someone

709
00:37:06,740 --> 00:37:08,010
who is the disturbing one.

710
00:37:09,700 --> 00:37:10,580
And it's my pleasure

711
00:37:11,460 --> 00:37:12,460
that I've played that role

712
00:37:13,290 --> 00:37:14,220
for the past three years.

713
00:37:40,440 --> 00:37:43,700
[Tieyuan No. 3 Middle School]

714
00:37:43,700 --> 00:37:43,790
Three, two, one.

715
00:37:43,790 --> 00:37:48,730
[Aim Higher, Youth Dream Deserved]

716
00:37:48,730 --> 00:37:51,450
Come here, Mr Wu.

717
00:37:51,540 --> 00:37:53,000
-Hurry up.
-Come here.

718
00:37:53,090 --> 00:37:53,970
Come on.

719
00:37:54,290 --> 00:37:56,370
Please join us.

720
00:37:56,930 --> 00:37:58,780
Let me dress up to look better.

721
00:37:59,250 --> 00:38:00,860
-Come on.
-Okay, everyone, look at the camera.

722
00:38:01,860 --> 00:38:03,620
Three, two, one.

723
00:38:05,850 --> 00:38:07,170
One more, please.

724
00:38:07,260 --> 00:38:09,370
Three, two, one.

725
00:38:09,780 --> 00:38:11,450
My right side looks better.
Take one more picture.

726
00:38:12,310 --> 00:38:13,210
Come.

727
00:38:13,420 --> 00:38:16,010
Three, two, one.

728
00:38:17,330 --> 00:38:18,210
Okay, good job.

729
00:38:18,330 --> 00:38:19,330
Go on, I'm leaving.

730
00:38:19,820 --> 00:38:21,810
Take care, Mr Wu.

731
00:38:22,100 --> 00:38:23,250
See you again.

732
00:38:26,180 --> 00:38:27,380
["To Li Qing Tong.]

733
00:38:28,290 --> 00:38:30,580
[A yellow shirt and a green feather inserted
in the hat, here comes Huo Qing Tong.]

734
00:38:31,340 --> 00:38:34,370
[This is the first thing I thought of
when I saw your name.]

735
00:38:35,250 --> 00:38:37,370
[You are a brave and unrestrained girl]

736
00:38:37,650 --> 00:38:40,580
[who is similar to Huo to some extent.]

737
00:38:41,380 --> 00:38:43,580
[Huo Qing Tong is perfect but pathetic,]

738
00:38:44,090 --> 00:38:46,810
[but Li Qing Tong is ordinary but happy.]

739
00:38:47,450 --> 00:38:49,890
[I hope this happiness
will always be with you.]

740
00:38:50,250 --> 00:38:51,650
[No matter what happens,]

741
00:38:52,010 --> 00:38:53,370
[you'll always be happy."]

742
00:38:53,470 --> 00:38:56,370
[Li Qing Tong]

743
00:39:01,450 --> 00:39:02,650
["To Li Jin Bu.]

744
00:39:03,770 --> 00:39:07,130
[You're the most special child
I've seen during my seven-year career.]

745
00:39:07,460 --> 00:39:09,090
[Firm but sensitive,]

746
00:39:09,170 --> 00:39:10,770
[gentle and violent.]

747
00:39:11,210 --> 00:39:14,290
[Under your tender appearance,
there is a subtle mind.]

748
00:39:14,850 --> 00:39:16,720
[You always say you're not likeable]

749
00:39:16,810 --> 00:39:18,100
[which is not important in fact.]

750
00:39:18,690 --> 00:39:20,610
[We don't need everyone to like us.]

751
00:39:21,250 --> 00:39:22,890
[Only the right people is enough.]

752
00:39:23,270 --> 00:39:24,150
[For you,]

753
00:39:24,260 --> 00:39:26,170
[you will never lack such people.]

754
00:39:26,450 --> 00:39:28,050
[They are all standing with you,]

755
00:39:28,140 --> 00:39:29,660
[not far away".]

756
00:39:30,010 --> 00:39:32,610
[Li Jin Bu]

757
00:39:36,680 --> 00:39:38,160
[Li Qing Tong]

758
00:39:47,380 --> 00:39:48,260
Ba Dan.

759
00:39:51,460 --> 00:39:52,930
Hua. Come here.

760
00:40:00,080 --> 00:40:11,880
[We've graduated!]

761
00:40:12,000 --> 00:40:14,570
[True Feeling Expression]

762
00:40:14,570 --> 00:40:16,290
[Black and White Death Demons
Taken Into Custody]

763
00:40:22,220 --> 00:40:24,060
[Cell phone]

764
00:40:24,060 --> 00:40:26,370
[Slam Dunk]
[Is society messy? It's Ba Dan's call]

765
00:40:32,210 --> 00:40:35,570
[We've graduated!]

766
00:40:44,500 --> 00:40:45,930
How could this happy mood

767
00:40:46,650 --> 00:40:49,050
be gone in not even two days?

768
00:40:52,130 --> 00:40:53,060
Yeah.

769
00:40:54,530 --> 00:40:56,640
How can this be different
from the scenes on TV?

770
00:40:56,730 --> 00:40:59,570
Other people's graduation is colourful.

771
00:40:59,660 --> 00:41:01,600
Why did we feel happy only
those days when we graduated?

772
00:41:01,690 --> 00:41:04,240
How can we feel nothing so soon?

773
00:41:04,330 --> 00:41:06,120
Can this compare with the scenes on TV?

774
00:41:06,210 --> 00:41:07,610
Those are fake.

775
00:41:07,940 --> 00:41:10,200
We don't know how many marks we'll get.

776
00:41:10,290 --> 00:41:12,720
When I think of those two
unanswered math questions,

777
00:41:12,810 --> 00:41:14,050
I even don't want to live.

778
00:41:14,620 --> 00:41:15,730
I'm just fine.

779
00:41:15,810 --> 00:41:17,610
I have a lot of unanswered questions,

780
00:41:17,700 --> 00:41:18,820
but I'm relieved.

781
00:41:19,050 --> 00:41:20,610
When I think about the score,

782
00:41:21,290 --> 00:41:23,330
I hate life even more.

783
00:41:25,930 --> 00:41:28,330
You have to fill in your dream school
after the score.

784
00:41:29,130 --> 00:41:32,460
Then wait for the examination result.

785
00:41:32,900 --> 00:41:36,250
Then wait for your admission letter.

786
00:41:36,660 --> 00:41:38,500
After that,

787
00:41:39,300 --> 00:41:41,610
it's time to go to college.

788
00:41:42,260 --> 00:41:43,930
You don't have to be so optimistic,

789
00:41:44,020 --> 00:41:46,010
you may miss the last two steps.

790
00:41:46,100 --> 00:41:46,980
Shut up.

791
00:41:48,740 --> 00:41:52,260
We can only wait day by day?

792
00:41:52,820 --> 00:41:56,850
Is this still the wonderful
graduation season at the age of 18?

793
00:41:57,810 --> 00:42:01,820
That is for those who study well.

794
00:42:02,180 --> 00:42:04,290
For those
who are good-for-nothing like us,

795
00:42:04,380 --> 00:42:06,370
after the score,

796
00:42:06,730 --> 00:42:10,240
life will go downhill.

797
00:42:10,330 --> 00:42:13,690
No need to wait.
I got one course evaluated.

798
00:42:14,180 --> 00:42:16,370
I'm already in the wind and rain.

799
00:42:18,970 --> 00:42:20,220
Let's go on a graduation trip.

800
00:42:21,980 --> 00:42:23,620
Yes! I agree.

801
00:42:24,450 --> 00:42:25,320
Let's travel around first.

802
00:42:25,410 --> 00:42:26,490
Right.

803
00:42:27,900 --> 00:42:28,780
Xiao.

804
00:42:36,450 --> 00:42:37,330
Is that beautiful?

805
00:42:38,020 --> 00:42:38,900
Yes.

806
00:42:39,730 --> 00:42:41,660
I said let's go on a graduation trip.

807
00:42:44,130 --> 00:42:45,410
I know an old village

808
00:42:45,500 --> 00:42:46,560
with beautiful scenery,

809
00:42:46,650 --> 00:42:47,730
it can be so fun.

810
00:42:48,380 --> 00:42:49,450
Really?

811
00:42:50,290 --> 00:42:51,490
Fine, let's go there.

812
00:42:52,050 --> 00:42:53,170
Let's go tomorrow.

813
00:42:54,050 --> 00:42:54,930
Or in a few days.

814
00:42:55,020 --> 00:42:55,900
Every day is a good choice.

815
00:42:56,000 --> 00:42:56,880
Good.

816
00:42:57,450 --> 00:42:59,120
We haven't heard from Wu Zhi Xun
in a long time.

817
00:42:59,210 --> 00:43:00,580
Would you like to ask him to join us?

818
00:43:02,410 --> 00:43:04,690
I've remembered something
when you mentioned Wu Zhi Xun.

819
00:43:04,780 --> 00:43:05,720
I heard that

820
00:43:05,810 --> 00:43:07,330
Wu Zhi Xun didn't take
the college entrance examination.

821
00:43:10,090 --> 00:43:10,970
What?

822
00:43:11,170 --> 00:43:13,650
I know it's hearsay only.
I don't know the detail.

823
00:43:15,370 --> 00:43:16,250
That's impossible.

824
00:43:16,930 --> 00:43:18,090
How is that possible?

825
00:43:19,770 --> 00:43:21,570
I'd believe whoever you say didn't take
the college entrance examination.

826
00:43:22,060 --> 00:43:23,650
